text: Wang Jianan (born 20 January 1983) is a Congo table tennis player. At the 2016 Summer Olympics he competed in the Men's singles. ==References== Category:Olympic table tennis players of the Republic of Congo Category:Chinese emigrants to the Republic of the Congo Category:Sportspeople of Chinese descent Category:1983 births Category:Table tennis players at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Living people Category:Republic of the Congo table tennis players Category:African Games gold medalists for the Republic of the Congo Category:African Games medalists in table tennis Category:Table tennis players from Baoding Category:Naturalised table tennis players Category:African Games bronze medalists for the Republic of the Congo Category:Competitors at the 2015 African Games
title: Wang Jianan (table tennis)
